  66:BSP/rc522_platform_stm32.c ****  *        - و•°وچ®هœ? SCK ن¸ٹهچ‡و²؟هڈ‘é€? (MOSI و›´و–°)
  67:BSP/rc522_platform_stm32.c ****  *        - و•°وچ®هœ? SCK ن¸‹é™چو²؟وژ¥و”? (MISO é‡‡و ·)
  68:BSP/rc522_platform_stm32.c ****  *
  69:BSP/rc522_platform_stm32.c ****  *        و—¶ه؛ڈ:
  70:BSP/rc522_platform_stm32.c ****  *        for 8 bits:
  71:BSP/rc522_platform_stm32.c ****  *            SCK = LOW
